'''杰斐遜港'''（Port Jefferson<ref>{{cite web|last=Glowatzwrite |first=Elana |url=http://www.northshoreoflongisland.com/Articles-News-i-2012-04-19-92129.112114-sub-Port-Jeff-Village-board-unanimously-approves-budget.html |title=Port Jeff Village board unanimously approves budget |publisher=Northshoreoflongisland.com |date=2012-04-19 |accessdate=2012-04-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130821093157/http://www.northshoreoflongisland.com/Articles-News-i-2012-04-19-92129.112114-sub-Port-Jeff-Village-board-unanimously-approves-budget.html |archivedate=2013-08-21 }}</ref>）是一個薩福克縣法人村，位於[[紐約|紐約]]北岸[[長島|長島]]的[[布魯克海文國家實驗室|布魯克海文國家實驗室]]。截至2010年美國人口普查，人口為7,750<ref name="Census 2010">{{Cite web| url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/DEC/10_DP/G001/1600000US3659355| title=Geographic Identifiers: 2010 Demographic Profile Data (G001): Port Jefferson village, New York| publisher=U.S. Census Bureau, American Factfinder| accessdate=2012-12-21}}</ref> 。村里有一些獨特的餐廳和商店，並有越來越多的[[旅遊業|旅遊業]]。

